trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid"></xref> column that hosts <xref:System.Uri> elements in its cells.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid"> </xref> kolonnen som er vert for <xref:System.Uri>elementer i celler.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: Use DataGridHyperlinkColumn to display data that contains a <xref:System.Uri>, such as an HTTP address or e-mail address.
trans-unit.target: Bruk DataGridHyperlinkColumn til å vise data som inneholder en <xref:System.Uri>, for eksempel en HTTP-adresse eller e-postadresse.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: The following illustration shows an example of a DataGridHyperlinkColumn.
trans-unit.target: Illustrasjonen nedenfor viser et eksempel på en DataGridHyperlinkColumn.

trans-unit.source: ![DataGridHyperlinkColumn with email addresses](~/add/media/wpf-hyperlinkcolumn.png "DataGridHyperlinkColumn with email addresses") > [!NOTE] > <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> navigation can only occur if either the direct or indirect parent of a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> is a navigation host.
trans-unit.target: ![DataGridHyperlinkColumn med e-postadresser](~/add/media/wpf-hyperlinkcolumn.png "DataGridHyperlinkColumn med e-postadresser") > [!NOTE] > <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>Navigasjon kan bare oppstå hvis en direkte eller indirekte overordnede en <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>er vert for navigasjon.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>

trans-unit.source: Examples of navigation hosts include <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, or any browser that can host [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)], such as [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie6](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie6-md.md)] or later and Firefox 2.0 or later.
trans-unit.target: Eksempler på navigasjon verter <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, eller en nettleser som er vert for [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)], slik som [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie6](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie6-md.md)] eller nyere og Firefox 2.0 eller senere.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the "Navigation Hosts" topic in [Navigation Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon, se emnet "Navigasjon verter" i [navigasjon oversikt over](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: To populate the column, bind the column to the <xref:System.Uri> data by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: For å fylle ut kolonnen binde kolonnen til den <xref:System.Uri>data ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A> </xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: To display hyperlink text that is different than the URI string, bind the text value to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn.ContentBinding%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil vise hyperlink tekst som er forskjellig fra URI-strengen, binde tekstverdi som den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn.ContentBinding%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn.ContentBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A> property is applied to the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> element created in the column.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>egenskapen gjelder den <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>eller <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>element som er opprettet i kolonnen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A> for the element in each cell is the data item for the row the cell is in.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A>Elementet i hver celle er dataelementet for rad cellen er.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, to set up the binding you only have to set the <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Path%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Derfor for å konfigurere bindingen trenger du bare å angi <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Path%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Path%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Optionally, you can specify a <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Converter%2A?displayProperty=fullName> if you want to convert the data.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil, kan du angi en <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Converter%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Hvis du vil konvertere dataene.</xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Converter%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For more information about data binding, see [Data Binding (WPF)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om databinding [Binding (WPF)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > DataGridHyperlinkColumn creates a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> element in the non-editing mode and a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> element in the editing mode.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > DataGridHyperlinkColumn oppretter en <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>element i modus for ikke-redigering og en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>element i modus for redigering.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>

trans-unit.source: If you want to display other types of data, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid> provides the following column types: |Column Type|Data Display| |-----------------|------------------| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn>|Use to display Boolean data.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn>|Use to display enumeration data.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn>|Use to display text.| If you want to use other controls in your <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>, you can create your own column types by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil vise andre typer data, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>gir følgende kolonnetyper: | Kolonnetypen | Vis data | |-----------------|------------------| | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn>| Bruk til å vise boolsk data. | | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn>| Bruk til å vise opplisting data. | | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn>| Bruk til å vise tekst. | Hvis du vil bruke andre kontroller i din <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>kan du opprette dine egne kolonnetyper ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>
